snippet.title: Midnight Scenes Ep.2. A short game by Octavi Navarro.
snippet.description:
Looking for a short, spooky adventure game to play this Halloween season?
Get the second episode of Midnight Scenes for free on:
https://octavinavarro.itch.io/midnight-scenes-the-goodbye-note

Keep updated about my new short games by subscribing to my mail list:
http://eepurl.com/drCjuH

And don't forget to subscribe to my Youtube channel!!! :)
Thanks for your support!

You can follow me on:
Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/OctaviNavarro
Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/octavinavarroAG
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/octavi_navarro 

Octavi Navarro. 2018.
http://www.octavinavarro.com
